sketch.compiler.passes.lowering

Class GlobalsToParams

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.FEReplacer
      • sketch.compiler.passes.lowering.GlobalsToParams
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    FEVisitor

    public class GlobalsToParams
extends FEReplacer
    convert global variables to inout parameters, with a static initializer function. deletes all global variables afterwards. 
     int G = 4;
 int G2 = ??;
 
 void fcn()
      x = G;
      G = ??;
    to 
     void fcn(ref G)
 
 void getGInitial() { return G; }
 
 main implements ...
     G = getGInitial()
     fcn(G)
    Author:
    gatoatigrado (nicholas tung) [email: ntung at ntung]
